Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要给度西斯反击的空档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快准备发射，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.68,0:00:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下驾崩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.72,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.46,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和宰相同归于尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装弹完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒸汽压上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.24,0:00:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下已经驾崩\N安那托勒只能靠我们来死守了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阁下，是乌尔班号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌尔班号…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.68,0:00:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.60,0:01:07.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.90,0:01:11.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.57,0:01:18.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.84,0:01:25.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.46,0:01:39.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.37,0:01:54.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.81,0:02:02.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.09,0:02:09.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.19,0:02:20.07,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}备齐材料\NMaking material
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.87,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨炮\N似乎已经进入发射准备状态了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪炮长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼雷瞄准定位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标，潘朵拉巨炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一号二号装弹完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信号弹，发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌尔班发出了信号弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以公主殿下之名\N命全军立刻停止作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下好像在乌尔班号上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经自认是皇帝了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父王明明才刚驾崩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大不敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把乌尔班号\N和度西斯舰队一起轰掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样公主殿下会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚殿下，就请您为\N安那托勒的重生而牺牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六号准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七号准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.38,0:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八号准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.25,0:03:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨炮\N正持续进行发射准备中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射鱼雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨炮确定已爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯舰队后方\N有其他舰队正在接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来的真是时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这停战命令…到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，后方有舰队接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去确认对方身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候\N和麦德赛侯爵达成串连的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这人的好处就是应变得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麦德赛舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前仍在接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，这是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一来停战命令\N根本就失去了意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备迎击敌方炮火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信号确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开战还是要撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请作选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，请下令开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除攻击准备，撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯舰队及其地上部队\N开始撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来对方司令官也了解\N骑士精神是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世界还是有救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您接下来可有得忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.13,0:05:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我们\N真的能把这里全部修好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别多嘴，给我惦惦干活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经连着三天彻夜工作\N几乎都没怎么睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上银之战舰\N现在就跟没穿衣服一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样怎么可能还去打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.46,0:06:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝他在担心生还章的运气\N是不是终于给用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们难道都不怕死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.66,0:06:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去找他好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说我搞不清楚\N克劳士他现在在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们吵架了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我单方面说出了想说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说我讨厌现在的克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出来后痛快多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也想了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.12,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过光是在那里想也不是办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是关于亚力克斯\N关于先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是关于塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些事情管它怎样都好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我喜欢先锋艇就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也希望能早一点让克劳士\N回头看看先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.52,0:07:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要退出吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是退出不坐先锋艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那架先锋艇\N是你父亲的不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是亚力克斯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要否定过去的自己好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你能用那架先锋艇\N飞越大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的梦想吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你\N感觉跟亚力克斯好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，打扰你们正开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问舰长大人在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…送货员吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西确实交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我跟渥卡问好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会替你转达的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你带路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进方向，地平洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解，前进方向地平洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.52,0:08:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将停留地平洞窟几天\N好作补给和修复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传达给相关单位知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们进行准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你们两位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.21,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你们送货到银之战舰来\N都不会觉得害怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难免吧，毕竟是五颗星任务嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过人家我可是送货的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是工作所需\N无论是哪儿我都会送去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不瞒你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好久没做这个工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为驾驶员不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.67,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这些本来该退休的老人\N这下也有工作找上门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来\N天空这东西真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子你也来飞飞看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很赞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.94,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以体会您的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对令尊的事情，我深感遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.52,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但陛下他已忘了天下苍生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王…已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.80,0:10:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了和你讨论今后的事情\N才来到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么有一件事必须要去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯的司令官是个明理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就以皇帝的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去见度西斯的司令官吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，要你跑这一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于要动手了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宰相吩咐要把关键谜诗交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.09,0:11:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这天我等了好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是达格贝家的关键谜诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将大地染作金黄的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将大地染作金黄的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一首\N宰相不是已经送来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不到知道的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长\N已到达地平洞窟的领空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰从现在开始\N即将进入地平洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行物资补给\N以及船身的修复作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.77,0:11:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前地平洞窟被开放为\N训练夺取组件作战用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.78,0:11:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒特殊部队的训练场地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.15,0:12:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已安排好大家可以自由使用\N他们的住宿设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请各自在出发前\N充分作好养精蓄锐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.86,0:12:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，下一排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.67,0:12:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地平洞窟…那里是干什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.84,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是对总帅大人您不敬的\N一群下等人的根据地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些下等战舰\N已开始集结在该洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表现出一些不甚安分的举动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许他们正企图破坏\N戴芬妮大人您的荣华…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭他们做得到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.92,0:13:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人提议说\N要不要早点把组件收回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一来便能轻易阻止\N谋反的发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不知何时会消失的翅膀来飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必一定很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在就把组件收回来\N就太没意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的就是那最精彩的一瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这你懂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可悲的人们哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是…算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从沙漠回来以后\N你变得很爱管闲事耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.29,0:13:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望你能在天上飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.03,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以一名战斗机驾驶员的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就不喜欢这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这就叫多管闲事知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在拉薇她正在修先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.72,0:14:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…现在不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因…因为我在忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和艾丽丝蒂亚去吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和大家一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那小子\N会和小公主在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.14,0:14:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是因为有过什么\N所以关系匪浅啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你厉害，小公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢，要不要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我解决完这个以后再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就这样走掉不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就体谅人家一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.12,0:14:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，你怎么那么迟钝\N走了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝到哪儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪兵不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.01,0:15:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，你来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这儿变得还真是通风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,采光又好，住起来挺舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都得感谢那位总帅大姊才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟，说到你的痛处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生下手也太狠了一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.43,0:15:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我来把它修得跟新的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有劳你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.80,0:15:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我听说\N请款单是开给皇宫是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也满不简单的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，那东西终于弄好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.38,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不和葛温他们一起去吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么我都想来这里看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是很喜欢先锋艇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在苦恼什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.14,0:16:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出来，你的表情怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪到不行\N根本不像平常的克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尔夫！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和我们认识的一个人\N长得实在太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那个机首像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.68,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一位叫做\N拉尔夫．温斯地的驾驶员给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一根哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尔夫是我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.30,0:17:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能接下我的任务…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.78,0:17:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇驾驶员和先锋艇一起\N被炸得连影子都不剩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他这也算是求仁得仁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要代我弟弟谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮他完成了他的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时没有想太多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个就给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望由你来保有它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.37,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由你这位先锋艇驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.77,0:18:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来在不知情里\N我也算是在为弟弟报仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说这是特殊部队\N到底都是在做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在演习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以安那托勒的宰相\N当初逃出基尔特时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所搭乘的战舰为攻击练习目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.46,0:18:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟以先锋艇去攻击战舰\N怎么说都是空前之举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒的先锋艇驾驶员\N几乎都被网罗来此了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.47,0:18:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是为此而来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.77,0:18:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋风霍克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖胖鸡！阳光男孩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋风霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋风霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还以为你一定没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好你也没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:19:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说诺齐亚被度西斯占领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不可能会为了这点小事\N而放弃飞行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，赖床宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是克劳士吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖胖鸡，阳光男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.98,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…感觉好像少了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫我鼻毛小子吧\N那样才像你嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会那样叫你的是拉薇啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，拉薇她怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫她来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…说来话长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛吞吞吐吐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想把这个秀给你瞧瞧的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是诺齐亚杯的冠军奖章吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，吓到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还不是因为当时\N我和克劳士退出了比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这根本就是狗屎运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你们怎么说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是本大爷赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很讨人厌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后他一直就这德性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.59,0:20:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，鼻毛小子，大肥鸡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧，旋风霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是少了这个\N怎么能叫做和你们重逢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的赞助者\N可是诺齐亚的麦德赛侯爵哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦德赛！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.22,0:20:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N诺齐亚的人都吓了一大跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据麦德赛侯爵的说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.65,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新时代的战争\N将要靠先锋艇来主导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说是在米纳纪斯会战里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架送货的先锋艇\N在战场上大出风头的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就是当时的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为这次攻击基尔特的行动\N带来了不少启示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的送货员\N该不会就是你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.11,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.84,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有因为肚子饿得\N而睡不着觉过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.65,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,什么骑士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.15,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,全是放屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.22,0:21:01.21,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,去做我们能做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能是他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.24,0:21:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诺齐亚的天空\N可是我们的地盘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么送货的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么新的战争…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.82,0:21:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只不过是\N拼命把工作做好而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亏我们还那么抗拒\N先锋艇被当成战争的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们…难不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时我只认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是先锋艇的话\N应该可以做些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N只有先锋艇能做到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到却把大家\N卷入了战争的天空下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是克劳士你一个人的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我把大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.19,0:22:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不能再逃避这片天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.49,0:22:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能再逃避先锋艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.34,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.95,0:22:46.01,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.09,0:22:57.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.23,0:23:02.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.84,0:23:11.54,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.55,0:23:23.29,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.36,0:23:29.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.23,0:23:34.93,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.01,0:23:46.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.23,0:23:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回预告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.93,0:23:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呜…英麦曼他讨厌我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.00,0:23:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样，鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.93,0:23:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是刚才那段话\N说的不得体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.13,0:24:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.77,0:24:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得满好记又好听呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.58,0:24:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最后流亡 第18话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚升级\NPromotion Sophia
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.48,0:24:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你与我是两颗流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.08,0:24:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起变成流星吧，英麦曼
